<para>This function can be used to inject a fault in either: </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>An address bit of a memory or memory mapped register address for any read or write access on AXI or LMB. </para></listitem>
<listitem>
<para>A data bit written to memory or a memory mapped register on AXI or LMB, as well as output on an AXI Stream. &lt; </para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>InstancePtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
